'''大巴扎''' ([[波斯语|波斯语]]: Bazar Bozorg, بازار بزرگ) 是伊朗[[伊斯法罕|伊斯法罕]]一个历史悠久的集市, 又名"Qeysarriyeh Bazaar" ([[波斯语|波斯语]]: بازار قيصريه).也是中东最大、最古老的集市之一。这是一个两公里长的拱顶街道，连接新老城区。<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://archnet.org/library/sites/one-site.tcl?site_id=3945
 |title       = Bazaar at Isfahan
 |publisher   = Archnet.org
 |accessdate  = 2007-07-19
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20060226021613/http://archnet.org/library/sites/one-site.tcl?site_id=3945
 |archivedate = 2006-02-26
}}</ref>

其历史可追溯到11世纪。

大巴扎位于伊斯法罕老市中心，在[[伊玛目广场|伊玛目广场]]北段。正门叫 Qeisarieh ，你可以一直步行到伊斯法罕最古老的清真寺[[伊斯法罕聚礼清真寺|伊斯法罕聚礼清真寺]]（礼拜五清真寺），也是伊朗最古老的清真寺之一。<ref name="Ali Assari">{{cite journal|last=Assari|first=Ali|author2=T.M. Mahesh|title=Comparative Sustainability of Bazaar in Iranian Traditional Cities: Case Studies in Isfahan and Tabriz.|journal=International Journal on Technical and Physical Problems of Engineering (IJTPE)|date=December 2011|volume=3|issue=9|pages=18–24|url=http://www.iotpe.com/IJTPE/IJTPE-2011/IJTPE-Issue9-Vol3-No4-Dec2011/3-IJTPE-Issue9-Vol3-No4-Dec2011-pp18-24.pdf|accessdate=6 January 2013|archive-date=2018-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181222163420/http://www.iotpe.com/IJTPE/IJTPE-2011/IJTPE-Issue9-Vol3-No4-Dec2011/3-IJTPE-Issue9-Vol3-No4-Dec2011-pp18-24.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last=Assari|first=Ali|author2=T.M. Mahesh|title=Conservation of historic urban core in traditional Islamic culture: case study of Isfahan city|journal=Indian Journal of Science and Technology|date=January 2012|volume=5|issue=1|pages=1970–1976|url=http://www.indjst.org/archive/jan-12-web/34-jan12aliassari.pdf|accessdate=7 January 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027112204/http://www.indjst.org/archive/jan-12-web/34-jan12aliassari.pdf|archivedate=2012年10月27日}}</ref>

